NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Section::Changes - Add a CHANGES POD section

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
    In your "weaver.ini":

     [Changes]

DESCRIPTION
    Inserting information in distribution's "Changes" to main module's POD
    can be a convenience for your module users.

    Changes is parsed using CPAN::Changes and markup in text entries are
    currently assumed to be POD too.

SEE ALSO
    Pod::Weaver

    CPAN::Changes

